>>No!

00:12:39.216 --> 00:12:40.340 align:middle line:90%
>>What do you want from us?

00:12:40.340 --> 00:12:41.825 align:middle line:90%
[THUNDER CLAPPING]

00:12:41.825 --> 00:12:44.795 align:middle line:90%
>>Why is this all going wrong?

00:12:44.795 --> 00:12:47.765 align:middle line:84%
[SNIFFLES] We have
