lawn and knock on their door

00:16:12.180 --> 00:16:13.610 align:middle line:90%
at all hours.

00:16:13.610 --> 00:16:17.150 align:middle line:84%
And it just became a
hodgepodge of stuff, much of it

00:16:17.150 --> 00:16:24.450 align:middle line:84%
sealed records, but we basically
that most of this was made up.

00:16:24.450 --> 00:16:27.260 align:middle line:84%
And what wasn't was just an
exaggeration of some things.

00:16:27.260 --> 00:16:29.470 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Two cases that
you don't believe are real.

